B-> ATM
1.  Start
2. ask the user for the pin
3. checks the pin with if else conditionals.
4. if pin is wrong, wrong pin.
5. else
6. three options-> 1. check balance 2.withdraw  3. deposit
7. if user enters option 1 ->
8. Simply dis[play the balance
9. if option 2-> 
10.  first check if the balance is >= withdraw amount
11.     if condition is true
12.       then withdraw the amount and subtract the withdrawed amount from the balance.
13.     else -> withdrawal unsuccessfull.
14.   then finally print the updated balance
15.if option 3->
16. enter the amount u want to deposit
17. then simply update the balance with this deposited money by adding
18. stop